STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Latimar BYRDSELL, Defendant-Petitioner. C-800 September Term 2017
080475 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 4, 2018

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005356-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
